Java : UTF-16

In java for string we have 3 Class String, StringBuffer, StringBuilder

There are more advantage over array and arraylist. : More Function regarding string

String Class : Immutable : Cannot change : Automatically thread safe  


StringBuffer Object is thread safe class : We can use it when at multi-threaded enviroment  & when object is shared across multiple thread

StringBuilder : Used within Single thread :
			When :  Single threaded program which required mutable stirng is used

